item.title: Me - Snaacker
item.description: A simple developer, tiny dreamer and a funny lover in this big big world Where I'm from? Currently, I'm living in Karlskrona, Sweden for now, but I'm from Hanoi, capital of Vietnam. It's an old city, with little bit dusty and noisy. However, you will love it, I'm sure! What am I doing for now? I'm a tech lover, and want focus my hundred percent effort in making things. I used to working for big big company, but now I'm just an engineer in small startup.
